modifiedPropertiesIgnoredInEqualsAndHashCode

java.lang.Object modifiedPropertiesIgnoredInEqualsAndHashCode()
To execute a parametrized feature method, Spock needs at least one dataset. Since some domain objects will use all their properties in equals and hashCode comparisons, we must provide a default implementation with a property that anyway should be ignored.
